Theme + tokens (central-app/app/src/theme.ts)
- MUI primitives: `createTheme`, `ThemeOptions`, `MuiCssBaseline` styleOverrides.
- Custom work: Openreach brand palette exposed via `theme.openreach`, typography defaults aligned to Inter, and scrollbar styling that matches fibre accents.

Landing overview surface (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Scaffold/App - Landing Overview.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `Stack`, `Box`, `Typography`, `Paper`, `Chip`, `IconButton`, `Popover`.
- Custom work: Access summary banner with Info popover, responsive paper cards with program icons, and chip cloud for tool badges.

Top banner (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Scaffold/App - Top Banner.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `AppBar`, `Toolbar`, `Stack`, `IconButton`, `Avatar`, `Menu`, `MenuItem`, `Typography`.
- Custom work: Gradient chrome, profile avatar menu with theme-aware tokens, and action slot for contextual buttons.

Side navigation (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Scaffold/App - Side Nav.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `Drawer`, `Paper`, `Stack`, `List`, `ListItemButton`, `ListItemIcon`, `ListItemText`, `InputBase`, `IconButton`, `Tooltip`, `Chip`, `Divider`, `Typography`.
- Custom work: Searchable task-force tree with badge metadata, client build footer, and responsive brand theming (including fallback nav items).

Shared MUI table shell (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Shared Components/MUI - Table/MUI Table - Table Shell.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `Paper`, `Stack`, `Typography`, `Switch`, `Box`, `DataGrid`, `GridToolbarQuickFilter`, `GridPagination`, `GridFooterContainer`. Table height responsive to viewport, single internal scroll, and margin added for visual separation (all via MUI standard props/styles).
- Custom work: Density toggle context, guarded header checkbox interaction, optional quick filter toolbar, configurable empty state slot.
 - 2026-01-10 update: DataGrid `sx` refinements remove the light-mode halo behind sort icons, align sort icon color to brand (`theme.palette.primary.main`), and suppress ripple in header action areas. Enabled `autosizeOnMount` with `autosizeOptions` (include headers, exclude outliers) and preserved single-scroll container.

Selection helper (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Shared Components/MUI - Table/MUI Table - Selection Logic.ts)
- MUI primitives: `GridRowSelectionModel`, `GridCallbackDetails` from `@mui/x-data-grid`.
- Custom work: Keyboard-aware selection manager providing single-select by default with Ctrl/Cmd multi-select and Shift range selection.

Selection helper documentation (Central Library/Application - Logic/Selection Logic)
- Outline: Purpose, behaviours, modifier handling, integration checklist, and testing guidance.
- Custom notes: Explains how the hook reads visible row order from the DataGrid API and why anchor tracking matters for consistent Shift selection.

Task filter + date window (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Shared Components/MUI - Table/MUI Table - Task Filter Component.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `Paper`, `Stack`, `Box`, `TextField`, `FormControl`, `InputLabel`, `Select`, `MenuItem`, `Checkbox`, `Chip`, `Button`, `Divider`, `OutlinedInput`, `InputAdornment`, `IconButton`, `Popover`, `List`, `ListItemButton`, `ListItemText`, `ListSubheader`, `ToggleButton`, `ToggleButtonGroup`, `StaticDatePicker`, `LocalizationProvider`.
- Custom work: Keyword + multiselect filters feeding a draft query state, contextual shortcut list for the date popover (week and quarter jumps), preserved time controls, deferred Apply/Clear workflow, and bulk-select inputs with select/clear icon logic documented in `Central Library/Application - Logic/Input Icon - Logic`. Validation now enforces mutually exclusive search flows (exact-match global query vs. Division/Domain/Status trio), trims input before submission, surfaces inline helper text, and keeps the previous dataset visible when the form is cleared.
 - 2026-01-10 update: Status options now render as `CODE → friendly` using `TASK_STATUS_LABELS`. Grid layout ratios tuned (`2.2fr 1.4fr 2.4fr 2fr 1fr`) for the simple tab. Bulk-select defaults to "select" when nothing is chosen so the control is always available. Date shortcuts for forward/back ranges are anchored to the current system date to ensure predictable windows.

Task management reference page (central-app/app/src/Openreach - App/App - Scaffold/App - Pages/Operations Management/Task Management.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `Stack`, `Box`, `Typography`, `Chip` paired with the shared table shell.
- Custom work: Priority/status chip palettes, `TaskTableQueryConfig` integration, memoised owner options, and filter pipeline driving the shared DataGrid instance. Exact-match validation now feeds on a memoised token set so global searches only return if they match real IDs; substring checks were replaced with equality checks to keep data honest.

Suspense fallback + loaders (central-app/app/src/App.tsx)
- MUI primitives: `Stack`, `CircularProgress` (indirect via compiled asset), typography usage inside Suspense fallback.
- Custom work: Friendly "Loading..." copy plus lazy loading for every scaffold card.
